translation_raw_response_power_respect_o:
{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "As a chaplain addressing a moral matter, Vogler speaks with institutional and spiritual authority. The tone is firm, serious, and direct, reflecting his role as a moral guide while maintaining a professional and neutral level of respect toward the elderly Salieri.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "在上帝眼中，那是罪过。"
