{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "Vogler speaks with institutional authority as a priest, asserting his role to provide spiritual guidance. The tone is firm and professional, utilizing a direct but composed register that reflects his higher situational power while maintaining a neutral, non-confrontational level of respect.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "向我忏悔吧，我能为你带来上帝的宽恕。"
