{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "Todd and Neil are close friends and peers, so the interaction is informal and egalitarian. As Todd is playfully repeating a line from a play at Neil's urging, the translation should be energetic and theatrical while remaining grounded in their casual, friendly dynamic.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "呀，你果真在那儿吗？！"
