{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "As a Senator speaking to a prisoner, Gracchus holds clear social and institutional authority. The tone is direct, assertive, and business-like, reflecting his higher power status while maintaining a neutral, civil register. The translation uses standard pronouns and a firm conditional structure to convey the gravity of the political proposal.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "如果元老院为你进行审判，你愿意支持他们吗？你必须向我保证。"
}

{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "As a high-power ruler, the speaker employs a commanding and assertive tone, expressing his desires and authority over his subjects with ease. The register is intimate yet decisive, reflecting a neutral level of respect that bypasses formalities while maintaining a sense of personal dominance and ownership.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "真是悦耳的声音！明天，我要让市民们——我的子民——重返竞技场。众神在上，我累了。过来休息吧，今晚我们要好好庆祝。"
}

{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "As the Emperor, the speaker uses an authoritative and superior tone to dismiss the listener's feelings. The low respect level is expressed through a mocking and cold dismissal of the listener's past attachments, treating them as a triviality that has finally been suppressed.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "既然那种痴念已经彻底结束了。"
}

{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "Proximo, as the employer/owner, uses his higher power to issue direct commands and negotiate terms. The respect level is neutral, reflecting a pragmatic, transactional tone where he is trying to persuade the listener with incentives and blunt logic.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "可是，你非上场不可！到时分给你的钱不止三成！等我拿到钱……你只管倒地装死！你伤得太重没法真打，而且对方可是个杀人狂！"
}

{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "The speaker and listener interact as equals, allowing for a direct and slightly cynical tone. Narcissus speaks with the familiarity of a business partner who sees through Proximo's scheme. The language is informal and conversational, reflecting their shared history and mutual understanding.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "压力挺大啊，普罗希摩？这里头肯定有不少赚头。要不然，你哪舍得把我这种抢手货给扔了？"
}

{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "As the person in charge, Proximo uses an authoritative and insistent tone to dismiss the subordinate's skepticism. The language is direct and commanding, reflecting a master-to-servant or boss-to-athlete dynamic where the speaker expects compliance while maintaining a neutral, business-like level of respect.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "绝不是那回事！这都是为了你好！快点，把剩下的盔甲穿上！"
