}

{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "The speaker holds superior social and institutional power, dictating terms from a position of authority. The tone is assertive and persuasive, using direct commands to offer a deal. The respect level is neutral, maintaining a transactional and firm register without being overly polite or unnecessarily hostile.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "在公开场合支持我。只要你这样做，我就让你大富大贵，还你自由。我会归还你的家产。我知道为了离开这里，你愿意付出任何代价。支持我，你就自由了。好好想想，重获自由后，你打算做什么？"
}

{
  "power_respect_guidance_summary": "Proximo holds higher situational power over Cos, leading to a direct and authoritative tone. He uses a neutral level of respect, being firm and serious without being overly aggressive or polite. The translation reflects a grave warning from a position of control.",
  "translation_power_respect_only": "你知道昨晚发生了暴乱。现在骚乱又开始了，康茂德已经调遣了一支军队。你应该清楚自己在做什么……"
}

{
